snippet.title: Plaque Man for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

Plaque Man is a Pac-Man clone, with a twist.

Plaque monsters attacked your teeth and they became yellow. Now you have to clean the teeth with your toothbrush to make them white again. Some teeth won't become white easily though, so you have to press the fire button to brush harder.

Plaque monsters can destroy the toothbrush, but you can collect toothpaste to get temporarily invulnerability.


What I think:

Quite fun and unique Pac-Man game, but for some reason the toothpastes disappeared in level 2. I guess you can only use them in the game once?
